Program: Omnibus
Title: Bluebeard - Gilles de Rais
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376ktp
Last Broadcast Date: 09 May 1994
The story of Bluebeard and how the real life execution of Frenchman Gilles de Rais in 1440, whose name is linked to the story, could have been a miscarriage of justice.